column5: Rivers were packed today but still managed some Steel. Hope everyone played nice. Cheers
I love how those river fish look. One day I'll learn properly on how to catch them  Great job man, must feel great to fight those fish!   Mike
Great shot of this beauty steel silverstreak Thanks for sharing Leechman
very nice fish, good work!  i have only been out a couple times this season and like you said quite crowded but haven't seen or heard of any problems, keep up the good work all!
